 Bethesda 出版主管在与开发商合作 24 年后退休https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/bethesdas-head-of-publishing-retires-after-24-years-with-the-developer-3515894?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=bethesdas-head-出版商在与开发商合作 24 年后退休Imogen DonovanMon, 16 Oct 2023 16:19:38 +0000 Gaming NewsNewsVideo Game Culture https://www.nme.com/?p=3515894 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/bethesdas-pete-hines-retires-after-24-years.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/bethesdas-pete-hines-retires-after-24-years.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/bethesdas-pete-hines-retires-after-24-years-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/bethesdas-pete-hines-retires-after-24-years-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/bethesdas-pete-hines-retires-after-24-years-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/bethesdas-pete-hines-retires-after-24-years-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/bethesdas-pete-hines-retires-after-24-years-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “这不是我轻易或迅速做出的决定”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/bethesdas-head-of-publishing-retires-after-24-years-with-the-developer-3515894">贝塞斯达 (Bethesda) 出版主管在与开发者一起工作 24 年后退休，</a>这篇文章首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/bethesdas-pete-hines-retires-after-24-years.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/bethesdas-pete-hines-retires-after-24-years.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/bethesdas-pete-hines-retires-after-24-years-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/bethesdas-pete-hines-retires-after-24-years-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/bethesdas-pete-hines-retires-after-24-years-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/bethesdas-pete-hines-retires-after-24-years-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/bethesdas-pete-hines-retires-after-24-years-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/bethesda-softworks">Bethesda Softworks</a>高级副总裁兼出版主管 Pete Hines 今天（10 月 16 日）宣布退休。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/stalker-2-heart-of-chornobyl-preview-hands-on-3488629">《潜行者 2：切尔诺贝利之心》预览：残酷，但前景令人难以置信</a></strong></li></ul><p>海因斯于 1999 年受聘，最初他负责为贝塞斯达的游戏名册编写手册，后来在产品发布的营销和公共关系中发挥越来越重要的作用。</p><p> “24 年后，我决定我在 Bethesda Softworks 的日子已经结束了。我即将退休，并将开始人生激动人心的新篇章，探索兴趣和激情，尽我所能贡献我的时间，并花更多时间享受生活，”他<a href="https://twitter.com/DCDeacon/status/1713918172351308242">在给 X（fka Twitter）的一份声明中</a>说道。 </p><figure id="attachment_3492166" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3492166" style="width: 1252px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3492166" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/starfield-alex-hays-tribute.jpg" alt="" width="1252" height="795" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/starfield-alex-hays-tribute.jpg 1252w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/starfield-alex-hays-tribute-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/starfield-alex-hays-tribute-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/starfield-alex-hays-tribute-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/starfield-alex-hays-tribute-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1252px) 100vw, 1252px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3492166" class="wp-caption-text"> 《星空》图片来源：Bethesda Softworks</figcaption></figure><p> “这不是我轻易或迅速做出的决定，但在经历了一段令人惊叹的职业生涯，并最终以令人难以置信的<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/starfield"><em>《Starfield》</em></a>的推出而达到顶峰，感觉现在是时候了，”他继续说道。</p><p>他补充说，他仍将是贝塞斯达全球粉丝群的积极组成部分，他称贝塞斯达粉丝群是一个“令人难以置信的社区”。</p><p>最后，他表示，他对在 Bethesda Softworks 工作二十年期间共事的同事感到非常自豪，并且他将怀着“真正的兴奋”等待开发者的下一步发展。</p><p>贝塞斯达软件公司<a href="https://www.gematsu.com/2023/10/bethesda-softworks-senior-vice-president-and-head-of-publishing-pete-hines-to-retire" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在自己的信息中</a>谈到了海因斯的退休：“皮特的公众形象只是他在贝塞斯达的一小部分，尽管他代表我们的方式延续了他在这里培育的价值观：真实、​​正直和热情。 </p><figure id="attachment_3494831" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3494831" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3494831" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Starfield-Mantis-quest-puzzle.jpg" alt="星空螳螂任务谜题" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Starfield-Mantis-quest-puzzle.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Starfield-Mantis-quest-puzzle-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Starfield-Mantis-quest-puzzle-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Starfield-Mantis-quest-puzzle-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Starfield-Mantis-quest-puzzle-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Starfield-Mantis-quest-puzzle-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3494831" class="wp-caption-text"> 《星空》图片来源：Bethesda Softworks</figcaption></figure><p> “他的贡献对于将贝塞斯达及其工作室家族打造成今天的世界级组织至关重要。他的远见推动我们前进，他的辛勤工作激励着我们。”</p><p>在其他游戏新闻中，在粉丝发现其中存在多个错误后<em>，暴雪娱乐悄悄删除了<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/diablo-4">《暗黑破坏神 4》</a></em>即将更新<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/diablo-4-trailer-deleted-by-blizzard-after-fans-point-out-multiple-mistakes-3515874">的<em>《血色赛季》</em>的预告片</a>。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-new